      <title>卡多佐预计尼日利亚汇款将增至 120 亿美元：Thisday</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/cardoso-sees-nigeria-remittances-rising-to-12-billion-thisday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《今日报》报道，尼日利亚央行行长奥拉耶米·卡多佐表示，尼日利亚有信心每月吸引海外公民汇款 10 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/cardoso-sees-nigeria-remittances-rising-to-12-billion-thisday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 07:25:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国警告美国将对台湾最新武器销售作出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/china-warns-us-it-will-respond-to-latest-taiwan-weapons-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，在美国最新向台湾出售武器后，已向美国提出外交抗议，并保留采取报复的权利，此举加剧了中台群岛争端的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/china-warns-us-it-will-respond-to-latest-taiwan-weapons-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 05:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通货紧缩影响中国工业利润继续下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/china-industrial-profits-extend-declines-as-deflation-takes-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于通货紧缩压力削弱企业财务实力，9月份中国工业企业利润下滑速度比前一个月更快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-27/china-industrial-profits-extend-declines-as-deflation-takes-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 02:05:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储政策会议前夕经济增长和受风暴影响的就业数据将成焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/gdp-storm-impacted-jobs-numbers-to-set-table-ahead-of-fed-policy-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距美联储官员开会讨论适当的降息节奏还有一周时间，三份备受瞩目的报告预计将显示美国经济的潜在弹性和就业增长的暂时停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/gdp-storm-impacted-jobs-numbers-to-set-table-ahead-of-fed-policy-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易狂潮可能给做市商带来虚假的安全感</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/bond-trading-frenzy-risks-giving-market-makers-a-false-sense-of-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从表面上看，公司债券市场从未如此稳定和流动。在美国，9 月份的交易量创下了有史以来的最高纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/bond-trading-frenzy-risks-giving-market-makers-a-false-sense-of-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 18:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
